comments: Difficult to see whether you were testing English skills or IT skills or speed thinking?
the sentances that were possibly'good english' were still maddening to read
the words on a blank white screen made it slightly difficult to look at

It made it hard to read because the words came up so quickly. Maybe this was part of the challenge. But I definitely made some mistakes because of this, whereas if I had more time to read it I would've known the answers.
The speed at which the words flashed up on the screen was hard to follow at times.
I would be willing to contribute any further studies if I was asked and meet the researchers specifications/conditions.
